title: First State National Historical Park: Management
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Management             Management         Dedication Day - March 25, 2013 NPS Photo   First State National Historical Park was established by President Obama on March 25, 2013 as the 400th unit of the National Park System.  As such, it is managed by the same laws and regulations as other units of the National Park System by the National Park Service. Park Planning Staff & Offices
